@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJqdXdvbiIsImlhdCI6MTc4NDYyMTczNiwiZXhwIjoxNzg0NjI1MzM2fQ.V-d4wS03CMDnA9dPrgDfHnBRmYyk5H27QvBKPoO878
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juwon",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juwon",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 내 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 프로젝트 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "DevTask 만들기",
  "description": "두 번째 풀스택 프로젝트"
}

### 내 프로젝트 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 프로젝트 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 프로젝트 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/projects/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "DevTask 수정",
  "description": "프로젝트 설명 수정"
}

### 프로젝트 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Task 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "JWT 로그인 구현",
  "description": "로그인 성공 시 토큰 발급",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### Task 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### status만 필터
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks?status=TODO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### priority만 필터
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks?priority=HIGH
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### status + priority 둘 다 필터
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks?status=TODO&priority=HIGH
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### IN_PROGRESS Task만 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks?status=IN_PROGRESS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Task 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Task 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "JWT 로그인 수정",
  "description": "토큰 발급과 검증까지 구현",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "priority": "MEDIUM"
}

### Task 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}